About Event

​​Join us for a 45 minute core-focused training sesh led by Lupe, a certified group fitness instructor who specializes in bringing fun to fitness.

​We’ll kick things off with a yoga-based warm-up to fire up breath, mobility, and deep core engagement, then we'll dive into a timed interval core training designed to challenge your abs from every angle.

​Come & you might just walk out with a new pair of Stride socks 👀

​​RSVP and we’ll remind you to bring a yoga mat, your friends, vib
